{"word":"G4151 - πνεῦμα - pneûma - pnyoo'-mah - Ghost","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πνεῦμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pneûma</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pnyoo'-mah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Ghost</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆவி - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்"},{"paragraph":"1. a movement of air (gentle) blast"},{"paragraph":"2. the spirit, the vital principle by which the body is animated"},{"paragraph":"3. a spirit"},{"paragraph":"4. God's power and agency"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4154 - πνέω - pnéō - pneh'-o/4154\">G4154</a>; a <i>current</i> of air, that is, <i>breath</i> (<i>blast</i>) or a <i>breeze</i>; by analogy or figuratively a <i>spirit</i>, that is, (human) the rational <i>soul</i>, (by implication) <i>vital principle</i>, mental <i>disposition</i>, etc., or (superhuman) an <i>angel</i>, <i>daemon</i>, or (divine) God, Christ&rsquo;s <i>spirit</i>, the Holy <i>spirit</i>: - ghost, life, spirit (-ual, -ually), mind. Compare <a href=\"#/G5590 - ψυχή - psychḗ - psoo-khay'/5590\">G5590</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1606/1606\">G1606</a>, <a href=\"#/G2315/2315\">G2315</a>, <a href=\"#/G4151/4151\">G4151</a>, <a href=\"#/G4152/4152\">G4152</a>, <a href=\"#/G4153/4153\">G4153</a>, <a href=\"#/G4154/4154\">G4154</a>"}]}